    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed VANOS system, addressing critical longitudinal and torsional stress points common to the chassis. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential for optimal power distribution. While the exterior shows minor road-derived character consistent with its age, the mechanical core remains stout with consistent compression across all six cylinders and recent preventative rod bearing replacement. It is a mechanically sound, high-performance platform ready for the apex, retaining its original suspension geometry and communicative steering rack.",
