    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity to own a well-cared-for model that balances performance with everyday comfort. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, showing only the slight, honest wear consistent with careful driving. Inside, the cabin is a highlight; the upholstery is free of tears or stains, and the interior plastics remain crisp and unfaded. Mechanically, the car is in robust health, having undergone a recent multi-point inspection and a fresh oil change. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision. All electronic features, including the infotainment system and safety sensors, are fully operational. Included with the sale is a complete set of service records, proving this car has never missed a scheduled maintenance interval. It offers a tight, quiet ride that feels solid on the road, making it an ideal choice for someone seeking reliability without the new-car price tag.",
