    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I\u2019m selling my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks fantastic on the road. The ride is smooth, the interior is nice and clean, and it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin. I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have!",
